title: Endangered shark fins seized in H.K. shipment
text:
Endangered shark fins seized in H.K. shipment Wednesday, May 30, 2018 - 01:44
Shark fins from endangered species including the giant, placid whale shark were found in a Singapore Airlines shipment to Hong Kong in May, highlighting the widespread challenges the Chinese territory faces in regulating the trade. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
